STEP 1: Create Project Folder 

Open Terminal and run:

mkdir brute_force_detector
cd brute_force_detector


STEP 2: Create Main Python Files

touch app.py
touch detector.py
touch firewall.py
touch database.db


STEP 3: Create Sub-Folders
mkdir templates
mkdir static
mkdir logs


STEP 4: Create HTML, CSS, and Log Files
touch templates/dashboard.html
touch static/style.css
touch logs/auth.log


STEP 5: Add Test Log Data 

Open the log file:

nano logs/auth.log


Paste this:

Jan 7 10:01:12 server sshd[1234]: Failed password for root from 192.168.1.10 port 4444 ssh2
Jan 7 10:01:15 server sshd[1234]: Failed password for root from 192.168.1.10 port 4444 ssh2
Jan 7 10:01:18 server sshd[1234]: Failed password for root from 192.168.1.10 port 4444 ssh2



STEP 6: Verify Structure

Run:

tree
